title: 10/27 Fantasy Football Podcast: Start or Sit (NFC); Collins or Ajayi ROS?
description:
Recapping the Thursday night blowout (2:05) and wondering if Alex Collins is better than Jay Ajayi going forward ... Dave had a weird dream about Adam (8:33). Also, the impact of the injuries on the WAS offensive line, the No Touchdowns Club (16:44), Beat the Waiver Wire (18:40) and Week 8 Bold Predictions (22:28) ... HOU-SEA (24:15), SF-PHI (35:00), CAR-TB (42:00), DAL-WAS (49:14), CHI-NO (54:21), PIT-DET (58:45) and a FanDuel lineup ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
